      "parameters": {
        "content": "# Cold Email – Part 1: Initial Email\n\nReads leads from a Google Sheet, skips anyone already in the sequence, then sends a personalised cold email based on partner type. Runs on a schedule.\n\n📄 [Google Sheet](https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/162MmWKtj8bfhY4bf48Ld-o6Vbwba1V0qqi14vTDe49o/edit?gid=860761689#gid=860761689)\n\n---\n## 📽️[Workflow Walkthorugh](https://drive.google.com/file/d/1ZRmonCPyrW8Jw1Q8Be8_SLa4pY9b7IZs/view?usp=sharing)\n\n---\n## How It Works\n1. Pulls leads from the sheet → removes duplicates → validates Name + Email\n2. For each lead, checks Tracking sheet — skips if status is `sent`, `followup_1`, `completed`, `replied`, or `unsubscribed`\n3. Routes by `partner_type` → builds matching email\n4. Sends via ZeptoMail → logs to Tracking sheet → moves to next lead\n\n## Sheet Setup\n### Leads Sheet (Tab: *Test Response*)\n**You fill:** `Name`, `Email`, `partner_type` (`College` / `Influencer` / `Brand` / anything else)\n\n### Tracking Sheet (Tab: *Tracking*)\n**Auto-filled:** `Email`, `status`\n\n## Setup\n1. Import workflow into n8n\n2. Connect **Google Sheets** + **ZeptoMail** credentials\n3. Point both sheet nodes to your sheet\n4. Activate\n\n## Customise\nReplace these placeholders in each email node:\n- `[YOUR COMPANY]`, `[YOUR NAME]`, `[YOUR TITLE]`, `[YOUR PHONE]`, `[YOUR EMAIL]`\n- `https://calendly.com/REPLACE_WITH_CALENDAR_LINK`\n- Schedule time → edit Schedule Trigger node\n\n",
